  "texts": [
    "RQ1: What is the distribution of research articles on AI technologies in education in Nigeria published in high-impact scientific journals between 2008 and 2022?To accommodate diverse learning styles and abilities, adaptive learning technologies were added to the initial e-learning platforms.",
    "AI algorithms in these systems assessed student performance and customized course materials [10,66,67].",
    "Liverpool et al. [10] proposed integrating an e-learning program at a Nigerian higher education institution to enhance learning experiences.",
    "Their findings suggested that full integration would free institutions from traditional educational limitations.",
    "Lexcellent [66] supported this, highlighting its transformative potential [67] used existing intranet networks in Nigerian tertiary institutions to design and implement an intranet-based communication and e-learning system."
  ]
}